snippet.title: Patafour (Patapon 4 fangame) - Demo release date Trailer
snippet.description:
Make sure to visit Patafour Discord server for more! https://discord.gg/dawfDyM

After 8 months of incredibly intense work, we come back with an update!
Enjoy this short trailer that sums up all the features that have been introduced so far.
Along with the demo release I will upload a followup showcase video, where I will explain all the new changes, improvements and bug fixes. 

Stay tuned! PATA PATA PATA PON!
